    <title>"Secure Automation and Continuous Monitoring (SACM) Architecture", Nancy Cam-Winget, Brian Ford, Lisa Lorenzin, Ira McDonald, loxx@cisco.com</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-camwinget-sacm-architecture-00.txt</link>
